okay so i just got back today from my basic cadet school at san diego marine recruit depot. OMG it was one hard weekend. friday i got their at around 7:00 and boom already their in my face. and all the cadets are atanding At attention which is super hard on your feet and memorizing shit. man it was hard we were out their for about 2 hours. before we got to rest and prepare our beds. sleeping was difficult some of the more immature cadets were fooling around. damn i hate kids. man moring wasn';t easy eaiter. im up its godamnn 5:30 in the moring man whats wrong with this people. and boom they wake us up by slamming some metal onto the ground. not the most pleasent sound. so we run oustide and get ready for some running and push ups. okay im good at that. and from then until about 10:30 at night it was drill,study,drill,study etc.... damn i was tired. but this morning i was up almost slept standing up in one class which would have been bad in front of major really bad. so our parents come and we put on a little parade for them. and they annouce honor cadets. OMG im honor cadet for the whole damn school! WTF is someone bribing people so i get this. im not THAT good. damn  after a good luch at piont loma sea food i come home fall down onto my bed and sleep until about 10. but im back and ready to just chill cause although that was deffintly interesting im gald its over. supposed to hang with ben tommorw fun shit
